# ── Nivora Interiors — Environment Variables ──────────────────────────────────
# These are needed by the Express API (runs as a Netlify Function in production).
#
# On Netlify: paste each key/value into
#   Site configuration → Environment variables → Add a variable
#
# Locally: copy this file to .env (already gitignored) and the dev server
#   will pick it up automatically via dotenv.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

